<i>(Rick) Forgive me.</i>

761
01:35:16,227 --> 01:35:18,309
(music fades out)

762
01:36:23,149 --> 01:36:25,231
(faint string music)

763
01:36:26,070 --> 01:36:30,120
<i>(Rick) There's so much lave inside us.</i>

764
01:36:35,430 --> 01:36:36,955
<i>That never gets out.</i>

