773
01:38:12,473 --> 01:38:14,555
(faint string music)

774
01:38:18,794 --> 01:38:21,161
(Fr. Zeitlinger) <i>Seems you're alone.</i>

775
01:38:22,834 --> 01:38:24,359
<i>You're not.</i>

776
01:38:26,074 --> 01:38:30,318
<i>Even now,
He's taking your hand and guiding you</i>

777
01:38:30,474 --> 01:38:32,044
